  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras/01e221de206d2dad40245de881627cc1.avif?t=1748589400\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras_big/01e221de206d2dad40245de881627cc1.avif?t=1748589400 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>If you're a cat, call now!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tel   9999 - 9999 - 99999</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We’ll make your human’s dream come true.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>We do not accept human calls.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras/a6e30dc6f640cae4859849ad8b220ad8.poster.avif?t=1748589400\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras/a6e30dc6f640cae4859849ad8b220ad8.webm?t=1748589400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Shoot wildly in your dream!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ammo is free.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just keep shooting!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eventually, you’ll hit something… maybe?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras/5ce2c13fd2b2b4b3d866bdb4585de140.avif?t=1748589400\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras_big/5ce2c13fd2b2b4b3d866bdb4585de140.avif?t=1748589400 width=800 height=532 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Clear every ODDRooM in your dream and…?!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We’ll grant you <i>one</i> wish — seriously, anything!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You might get a raise!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You might become a better person!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You might wake up from a coma!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“Bring us CatCoins!!”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras/6546ef8ff9a0f1dd664783251ca09cf7.avif?t=1748589400\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras_big/6546ef8ff9a0f1dd664783251ca09cf7.avif?t=1748589400 width=800 height=532 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>In real life, you walk and shoot.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But in ODDRooM, you FLY and shoot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But beware…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You <i>can’t</i> get stronger without CatCoins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“Bring us CatCoins!!”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras/29dcc994b666da04facff8beae9d2f84.poster.avif?t=1748589400\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras/29dcc994b666da04facff8beae9d2f84.webm?t=1748589400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>So many weapons. So weird. So awesome.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We’ve got <i>more weapons than your grandma has teacups!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Random Weapon Vending Machine is totally fair.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(But we don’t do refunds… even for dumb weapons.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“Bring us CatCoins!!”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras/734417211701d5dc4dd0ed82f249287c.avif?t=1748589400\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras_big/734417211701d5dc4dd0ed82f249287c.avif?t=1748589400 width=800 height=532 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Swap your limbs!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why not? It’s a dream!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Octopus legs? Bone legs? All good.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t worry — <i>you can’t die!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras/514bba8dde12f53f7d900cdefde57860.avif?t=1748589400\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras_big/514bba8dde12f53f7d900cdefde57860.avif?t=1748589400 width=800 height=532 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Strength? Speed? Jumping? Kung fu?</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No sweat required.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With CatCoins, anything is possible in dreams.<br><strong>“Bring us CatCoins!!”</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras/d4d3a66306993ba8d2011c30dfe77ab1.avif?t=1748589400\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras_big/d4d3a66306993ba8d2011c30dfe77ab1.avif?t=1748589400 width=800 height=532 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Where do all the CatCoins go, you ask?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We use them for the <i>welfare of all cats everywhere.</i><br>Just… trust us.<br><strong>“Bring us CatCoins!!”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras/7883a65b74166f06dea30e4b02af7847.avif?t=1748589400\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795230/extras_big/7883a65b74166f06dea30e4b02af7847.avif?t=1748589400 width=800 height=532 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Sign the contract!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You don’t have to read the whole thing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cats trust each other, right?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Worried the monsters are too strong?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No, no… your human is just too weak.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“Bring us CatCoins!!”</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fine Print:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are not responsible for any side effects in dreams.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you don’t clear the dream…You <i>may never wake up again.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(But don’t worry — 3% of users <i>have</i> cleared it !! )</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
